# Generated by Cargo
# will have compiled files and executables
debug
target

# These are backup files generated by rustfmt
**/*.rs.bk

# MSVC Windows builds of rustc generate these, which store debugging information
*.pdb

# Generated by cargo mutants
# Contains mutation testing data
**/mutants.out*/

# RustRover
#  JetBrains specific template is maintained in a separate JetBrains.gitignore that can
#  be found at https://github.com/github/gitignore/blob/main/Global/JetBrains.gitignore
#  and can be added to the global gitignore or merged into this file.  For a more nuclear
#  option (not recommended) you can uncomment the following to ignore the entire idea folder.
.idea/

test_data/*
# Track only the small CI fixtures; larger fixtures stay local.
!test_data/btfl_all_old.bbl
!test_data/jeno_after.bbl
!test_data/tbs_after.bbl

# Track only the docs referenced from README / CLAUDE.md. Working notes,
# old auto-generated reports, and upstream parser refs stay local.
docs/*
!docs/PROJECT_ASSESSMENT.md
!docs/prd.md
!docs/technical-development-document.md

# Local Claude Code state (per-machine settings, transcripts).
.claude

# Artifacts the `tune` flow drops in the working dir.
tune-backup-*.json
drone-tuner-pull-*.bbl